__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    createFlexible:
      path: /flexible
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: FlexibleObject
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: FlexibleObject
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              name: name
    createStrict:
      path: /strict
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: StrictObject
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: StrictObject
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              name: name
    createStringMap:
      path: /string-map
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: StringMap
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: StringMap
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: id
    createObjectMap:
      path: /object-map
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: ObjectMap
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: ObjectMap
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            key: {}
          response:
            body:
              key:
                value: value
                count: 1
    createUserMap:
      path: /user-map
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: UserMap
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: UserMap
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            key: {}
          response:
            body:
              key:
                id: id
                name: name
    createArrayMap:
      path: /array-map
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: ArrayMap
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: ArrayMap
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            key:
              - value
          response:
            body:
              key:
                - value
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  FlexibleObject:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      name: optional<string>
    extra-properties: true
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  StrictObject:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      name: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  StringMap:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  ObjectMapValue:
    properties:
      value: optional<string>
      count: optional<integer>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true
  ObjectMap: map<string, ObjectMapValue>
  User:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      name: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  UserMap: map<string, User>
  ArrayMap: map<string, list<string>>

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Additional Properties Edge Cases
